{"tid":1356811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請緊記抗爭目的！","createTime":"2019-07-23T14:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T14:57:54.000Z","uid":271906,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f372cf557144d7bd80a4d6e186d685581993320","tid":1356811,"uid":271906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"7月21晚發生咩事，唔需多講。大家都好嬲。<br />\n727一定係入元朗<br />\n<br />\n但想提返大家我地嘅抗爭目的唔係打9班黑社會，黑警。佢地只係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煙幕</span></span>，中共只係想用不同方法令我地失焦。何妖只不過係佢地嘅一隻狗，邊撚到會有政棍明知民怨咁撚勁仲走出黎周圍講d on9野。佢就係想大家將焦點放係佢到。而共產黨成功左一半，721港島另一班戰友比人射都好似無人知無人理。<br />\n<br />\n麻煩大家記返我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5大訴求</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n同埋千其唔好比怒火沖昏頭腦。<br />\n對家最愈驚愈大反應就愈要攻，好似西環咁<br />\n敵進我退，敵退我進阿"},{"pid":"d854b6ef7f5558207743e81797e910820fe244d9","tid":1356811,"uid":271906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:56:02.000Z","msg":"推阿"},{"pid":"81f608da8e3f9b5a5fe15714c8fc9924d5f56c99","tid":1356811,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:56:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回送中條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n 6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"432c88ab5a813dbadbfa4ee5da8e7dbcdf7a960e","tid":1356811,"uid":279085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzfNKZRPQHZk&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4Xs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=75cbb31a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zfNKZRPQHZk</a>"},{"pid":"7507219ccb7f93e2d9e6c8ad1564adf2eb16392a","tid":1356811,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"平日示威、遊行、光復<br />\n都好和平，就算升級都只係破壞公物<br />\n唔會傷害無辜<br />\n<br />\n但元朗呢班清朝惡到而家嘅黑勢力唔係人咁品<br />\n嚇窒唔少和理非"}]}